Honestly I don't even think it's that nefarious like them suppressing cancer cures consciously or anything like that, being a pop science skeptic misinformation expert is just a very cozy fake job where you don't have to actually do anything and get paid well. Bolshevik Nepotism.

The most bizarre example is Mikhail Volkenstein who was the grandson of the lawyer who had initiated Lenin into freemasonry and defended him when he had been accused of crimes against the state and was supposed to be put in prison. Dmitry Galkovsky has a few lectures on this too.
